# Testing

- Domain/application tests use public interfaces and in-memory adapters at real seams.
- Repository tests run real {{.Database}} migrations and sqlc queries through Testcontainers.
- HTTP tests exercise the composed Echo/Huma application.
- Frontend tests use Vitest/Testing Library; browser flows use Playwright.
- `make verify-generated` is the local and acceptance-harness entrypoint.

Seed profiles are deterministic and idempotent. Run a selected profile twice in integration tests and verify behavior through authenticated public routes.
